description:
This is a 32 minute workout called '30MIN full body pilates workout (no equipment)' from the channel Lidia Mera.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Meditative Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate and Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: a 30-minute pilates class designed to make you feel energised and ready for the day ahead! Low-impact movements to help with flexibility, strength, and mobility. 

Hope you have fun doing this workout! 
Love you all, Lidi x
